snippet.title: FOLDY'S OS QUEST | Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3532060/Foldys_OS_Quest/

Introducing the first game from Vacation Home!

Foldy’s OS Quest invites players into a colorful computerized world for an action-packed 3D platforming adventure like no other! Run, jump, zip, surf and stomp your way through the magical world of personal computing, and take down the virus before it can break through the Firewall!

Coming soon!

https://www.vacationhomegames.com

#indiegame #indiedev
